highlights.text: “Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 941 days straight.
“ME POSTOU NO DAILY - FESTA DO BIG G” by MC GP, Mc Lele JP, DJ DAVI DOGDOG, and Dj Andrabeat is the highest new entry on Top Songs Brazil at #144.
Henrique & Juliano has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “Última Saudade - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #10.
“Every Breath You Take” by The Police is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 40 spots at #150.
